  <constraints>
    <constraint source="R5 reuse mandate (CLAUDE.md Â§3.1 + project CLAUDE.md Â§3.1)">MUST extend the existing `GetStartedCardsWidget` catalog; MUST NOT introduce a parallel welcome system, a parallel cards widget, a new shell stage, or a fork of `ContextPaneController` welcome-stage rendering.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent UI v9 semantic tokens only. No hex literals, no rgba literals. Dark-mode rendering MUST be visually correct â€” verify via `prefers-color-scheme: dark` or shell theme toggle.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-022">React 19 only. Use hooks; no class components; no React 18-only APIs.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-025">All Fluent icons sourced from `@fluentui/react-icons` v9. Reuse `DocumentMultipleRegular` if appropriate or pick a v9 icon distinct from the existing "Summarize Files" card per design intent (a separate visual entry).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-028">No `accessToken` props or state in this widget. The widget invokes only the existing `onCardClick` callback; chat-pane handlers own auth.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-030">PaneEventBus closed at 4 channels. Adding the new card MUST NOT introduce a 5th channel. Existing event types (`widget_load`, additive R5 event types per project CLAUDE.md Â§3.4) are sufficient.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-031">Card visibility is gated by `useShellStage()` returning the welcome stage. The card MUST NOT render on non-welcome stages. Verify via the existing `ContextPaneController` welcome-stage branch â€” no new stage logic required.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project CLAUDE.md Â§3.2">R5 introduces NO new feature flag for this card. Visibility derives from existing stage logic, not from a configuration toggle.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-07 / CLAUDE.md Â§10">BFF publish-size delta = 0 MB. No BFF code is changed. Confirm in task notes; do NOT run `dotnet publish` (frontend-only change).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Click handler MUST open the chat-pane file upload dialog AND pre-fill the chat input with `/summarize ` (with trailing space). Both effects MUST be observable in a single user gesture.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">MUST NOT regress the existing 7-card `GetStartedCardsWidget` behavior â€” keyboard navigation (arrow keys + Enter/Space), 2-col-at-narrow / auto-fill-at-wide responsive grid, ARIA `role="grid"` + `role="gridcell"`, ActionCard primitive reuse, screen-reader card descriptions.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Discoverable parallel entry â€” the card is an ADDITIVE discovery affordance for the same flow `/summarize` ships. Click semantics MUST mirror what typing `/summarize` followed by a paperclip click would do in the chat pane.</constraint>
  </constraints>

